OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud soon clearing
OL,6,Fto leave a largely dry and bright day,
OL,7,Fwith occasional sunny spells,
OL,8,Fespecially during the morning.
OL,9,FBecoming increasingly cloudy and
OL,10,Fbreezier from the west into the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA band of rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes, will quickly move eastwards
OL,15,Facross all parts overnight, clearing
OL,16,Fby dawn. Becoming drier with clearer
OL,17,Fspells from the west. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
