OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA breezy day, although it
OL,6,Fshould be largely dry with bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Chance of a few showers
OL,8,Freaching western parts later in the
OL,9,Fday. Staying mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FBlustery and largely dry Thursday,
OL,13,Fbefore a band of rain, heavy and
OL,14,Fsqually, moves erratically southeast
OL,15,Fovernight, clearing to blustery
OL,16,Fshowers Friday. Feeling colder. Drier,
OL,17,Fbrighter and less windy Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
